         MACRO                                                                  
&L       TOD                                                                    
.*                                                                              
.*  Obtain local time in "MIC" format                                           
.*                 (STCK + local time of day offset)                            
.*                                                                              
         PSET  @TOD                                                             
&L       VCALL TOD                                                              
         MEND                                                                   
